room_title: Escape room "Murphy’s Law" by The LOST Escape Room in Charleston (WV)
room_address: 314 Goff Mountain Rd Cross Lanes, WV 25313
room_description: Today is the big day that crazy Uncle Murphy promised you. He’s taking you to get a ton of money he’s been saving for you since the 60s. Simple enough, right? Go with Uncle Murphy and let him get it for you. Hope for the best but expect the worst.
